Pandas Projects & Practice

This folder contains hands-on Python (Pandas) projects and practice notebooks focused on data cleaning, exploratory data analysis (EDA), and deriving business insights from real-world datasets.
These projects are part of my career transition into Data Analytics, built through structured learning and consistent practice.

